rald Alvestrand is chief executive officer of the organization.','zh-cn','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','This organization was created on May 1, 1999, taking over the running of the counter from Harald Tveit Alvestrand, who has been running the project since 1993. Harald Alvestrand is chief executive officer of the organization.','2015-04-13 22:27:12'),(628,'It was started as a \"for fun\" project to find out how many Linux users there are worldwide. The basic idea is for people to register themselves as being a Linux user.','zh-cn','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','It was started as a \"for fun\" project to find out how many Linux users there are worldwide. The basic idea is for people to register themselves as being a Linux user.','2015-04-13 22:27:12'),(629,'Of course, this way you won\'t get all Linux users counted as not every Linux user will register himself at the Linux Counter site.','zh-cn','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','Of course, this way you won\'t get all Linux users counted as not every Linux user will register himself at the Linux Counter site.','2015-04-13 22:27:13'),(630,'Thus, the only way to \"know\" the number of Linux users worldwide, is to make a guess, preferably a not-too-wild guess of the number of Linux users. Not making wild guesses there is only one way to go: statistics. And so, there we are.','zh-cn','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','Thus, the only way to \"know\" the number of Linux users worldwide, is to make a guess, preferably a not-too-wild guess of the number of Linux users. Not making wild guesses there is only one way to go: statistics. And so, there we are.','2015-04-13 22:27:13'),(631,'What is this all about?','zh-cn','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','What is this all about?','2015-04-13 22:27:13'),(632,'This is all about statistics. Statistics about Linux and its users. The main goal is to determine how many linux users there are worldwide.','zh-cn','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','This is all about statistics. Statistics about Linux and its users. The main goal is to determine how many linux users there are worldwide.','2015-04-13 22:27:13'),(633,'Is this really free of charge?','zh-cn','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','Is this really free of charge?','2015-04-13 22:27:13'),(634,'Yes, sure! Linux is free and so we are free too. This service is completly free of charge without any hidden costs or something.','zh-cn','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','Yes, sure! Linux is free and so we are free too. This service is completly free of charge without any hidden costs or something.','2015-04-13 22:27:13'),(635,'Is this service secure?','zh-cn','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','Is this service secure?','2015-04-13 22:27:14'),(636,'Of course it is. It is as secure as it can be with a great bunch of established and popular third party bundles, that are open source too.','zh-cn','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','Of course it is. It is as secure as it can be with a great bunch of established and popular third party bundles, that are open source too.','2015-04-13 22:27:14'),(637,'All of your private data is secured and safely encrypted in our database. You have the choice only by yourself to make your data (for example your email address) public or not.','zh-cn','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','All of your private data is secured and safely encrypted in our database. You have the choice only by yourself to make your data (for example your email address) public or not.','2015-04-13 22:27:14'),(638,'And even if your email address is public, it is secured by javascript and other methods to prevent bots from stealing it.','zh-cn','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','And even if your email address is public, it is secured by javascript and other methods to prevent bots from stealing it.','2015-04-13 22:27:14'),(639,'How ca