re are worldwide.','af','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','This is all about statistics. Statistics about Linux and its users. The main goal is to determine how many linux users there are worldwide.','2015-04-13 22:28:55'),(1111,'Is this really free of charge?','af','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','Is this really free of charge?','2015-04-13 22:28:55'),(1112,'Yes, sure! Linux is free and so we are free too. This service is completly free of charge without any hidden costs or something.','af','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','Yes, sure! Linux is free and so we are free too. This service is completly free of charge without any hidden costs or something.','2015-04-13 22:28:55'),(1113,'Is this service secure?','af','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','Is this service secure?','2015-04-13 22:28:56'),(1114,'Of course it is. It is as secure as it can be with a great bunch of established and popular third party bundles, that are open source too.','af','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','Of course it is. It is as secure as it can be with a great bunch of established and popular third party bundles, that are open source too.','2015-04-13 22:28:56'),(1115,'All of your private data is secured and safely encrypted in our database. You have the choice only by yourself to make your data (for example your email address) public or not.','af','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','All of your private data is secured and safely encrypted in our database. You have the choice only by yourself to make your data (for example your email address) public or not.','2015-04-13 22:28:56'),(1116,'And even if your email address is public, it is secured by javascript and other methods to prevent bots from stealing it.','af','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','And even if your email address is public, it is secured by javascript and other methods to prevent bots from stealing it.','2015-04-13 22:28:56'),(11