here are worldwide. The basic idea is for people to register themselves as being a Linux user.','2015-04-13 23:30:00'),(4868,'Of course, this way you won\'t get all Linux users counted as not every Linux user will register himself at the Linux Counter site.','sq','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','Of course, this way you won\'t get all Linux users counted as not every Linux user will register himself at the Linux Counter site.','2015-04-13 23:30:02'),(4869,'Thus, the only way to \"know\" the number of Linux users worldwide, is to make a guess, preferably a not-too-wild guess of the number of Linux users. Not making wild guesses there is only one way to go: statistics. And so, there we are.','sq','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','Thus, the only way to \"know\" the number of Linux users worldwide, is to make a guess, preferably a not-too-wild guess of the number of Linux users. Not making wild guesses there is only one way to go: statistics. And so, there we are.','2015-04-13 23:30:04'),(4870,'What is this all about?','sq','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','What is this all about?','2015-04-13 23:30:06'),(4871,'This is all about statistics. Statistics about Linux and its users. The main goal is to determine how many linux users there are worldwide.','sq','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','This is all about statistics. Statistics about Linux and its users. The main goal is to determine how many linux users there are worldwide.','2015-04-13 23:30:08'),(4872,'Is this really free of charge?','sq','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','Is this really free of charge?','2015-04-13 23:30:09'),(4873,'Yes, sure! Linux is free and so we are free too. This service is completly free of charge without any hidden costs or something.','sq','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','Yes, sure! Linux is free and so we are free too. This service is completly free of charge without any hidden costs or something.','2