f the number of Linux users. Not making wild guesses there is only one way to go: statistics. And so, there we are.','ta','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','Thus, the only way to \"know\" the number of Linux users worldwide, is to make a guess, preferably a not-too-wild guess of the number of Linux users. Not making wild guesses there is only one way to go: statistics. And so, there we are.','2015-04-14 07:48:08'),(12957,'What is this all about?','ta','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','What is this all about?','2015-04-14 07:48:11'),(12958,'This is all about statistics. Statistics about Linux and its users. The main goal is to determine how many linux users there are worldwide.','ta','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','This is all about statistics. Statistics about Linux and its users. The main goal is to determine how many linux users there are worldwide.','2015-04-14 07:48:14'),(12959,'Is this really free of charge?','ta','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','Is this really free of charge?','2015-04-14 07:48:17'),(12960,'Yes, sure! Linux is free and so we are free too. This service is completly free of charge without any hidden costs or something.','ta','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','Yes, sure! Linux is free and so we are free too. This service is completly free of charge without any hidden costs or something.','2015-04-14 07:48:20'),(12961,'Is this service secure?','ta','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','Is this service secure?','2015-04-14 07:48:23'),(12962,'Of course it is. It is as secure as it can be with a great bunch of established and popular third party bundles, that are open source too.','ta','syw_front_main_main_faq','anonymous','persist','Of course it is. It is as secure as it can be with a great bunch of established and popular third party bundles, that are open source too.','2015-04-14 07:48:26'),(12963,'All of your private data is secured and safely encrypted in our 